Introduction

Tejong is a South Korean singer-songwriter and musician known for his emotive vocals and acoustic-driven sound. He made his official solo debut on August 3, 2021, with the digital single “Pervert”. Self-managed and distributing through Poclanos, Tejong gained broader attention as Contestant #47 on Sing Again 3, where his heartfelt performances and poetic lyricism captivated audiences. He continues to build a dedicated following in Korea’s indie and ballad scene.
